  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>Yes</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Transcorneal stimulation may enable neurons to survive degeneration processes via enhanced
      secretion of neurotrophic substances and direct stimulation of neurons.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
